public interface ScheduleElement
extends TimeSpan

A ScheduleElement is an encapsulation of spatio-temporal relationships. Current thought is to bind up both time and space into a single object which may then be queried in various ways to test for overlaps, inclusion, exclusion, etc with other schedules.
